Package: languageserver
Type: Package
Title: An implementation of the Language Server Protocol for R
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2017-09-10
Author: Randy Lai
Maintainer: Randy Lai <randy.cs.lai@gmail.com>
Description: An implementation of the Language Server Protocol for R. The Language Server protocol is used by a client to integrate features like auto complete. See https://github.com/Microsoft/language-server-protocol/blob/master/protocol.md for details.
